tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
context: Wisdom Tooth Extraction,RCT - Root Canal Treatment,
review: I've always been dead scared of doctors n treatments. When I was explained about the need for RCT & wisdom tooth extraction, I thought I would be screaming in pain during treatment. But Dr.Supriya ma'am is everything a great dentist must be. With miraculous ease, top-notch treatment procedures and state of the art equipment, she made sure that I left the clinic with delight. Very peaceful, hygienic clinic. Highly affordable n transparent pricing. One would've never met a doctor with this much patience elsewhere. Very polite, passionate and admirable human. Not all heroes wear capes. She is a superhero in scrubs.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,
review: I would definitely recommend The Dental Experts to everyone I know for their dental problems. Dr. Supriya and team are professional in their approach and explain the procedure in detail and transparency maintained at every step that made me trust them.
